{"tid":272274,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有圖慎入 麥皮蟲死後岀現大量蛆蟲","createTime":"2017-06-05T16:48:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-05T20:41:21.000Z","uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4882e0f2ac9023d6909b50a226094a5049053306","tid":272274,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T16:48:28.000Z","msg":"前幾日買咗盒麥皮蟲 放咗入密封膠盒 可能因為天氣 又熱又濕 搞到岀倒汗水 全滅<br />\n之後就岀現咗啲大約1cm長嘅蛆蟲<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/06/004629_0875a97ced1ef87f6019cc8147c6c28e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F06%2F004629_0875a97ced1ef87f6019cc8147c6c28e.jpg&h=6e4707af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n透透地明 近水狀 隔住個盒都有味岀到嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即刻用膠紙封邊成個包住扔咗佢<br />\n<br />\n普通烏英嘅蛆蟲應該好細粒 呢啲應該係寄生蟲嚟 有無人知咩料"},{"pid":"ec59161bf0e233f684fd7174b9fd23958cafb573","tid":272274,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T16:50:01.000Z","msg":"連登仔新技能"},{"pid":"c095a590c2512f843f003f7ab217f96c0ee46859","tid":272274,"uid":3818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T16:50:04.000Z","msg":"巴打養咩蜥蜴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e83b4f3711d07495d72419d234a79dfa1d0b83b","tid":272274,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T16:51:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打養咩蜥蜴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n養蟻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d28aaf2e0cb7883956d4b84bc0ef257fe74e139","tid":272274,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T16:52:23.000Z","msg":"起碼有40條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/